posting_body: ['1-BR Apartment Listings:', '► 590 Holly, St. Paul -- 1BR', 'Apartments available July, August, or September', '-- 1st, 2nd, or 3rd (top) floor', '-- $985 - $1,025/mo', '-- Tenants pay electricity.', ' Property owner pays radiator heat, water, and stove gas!', '-- Great lease terms!', 'Flexible or Fixed.', 'Quoted rents are for a 9-12 month fixed term lease.', 'Additional $25/mo for flexible term.', '-- Smoke-Free!!!', ' All leases prohibit smoking, candles, and incense anywhere inside the building or on the property outside.', 'Two blocks north of Summit Ave (three blocks north of Grand Ave), you are close to the many shops and scenic areas St. Paul, MN, has to offer -- this residential neighborhood location is fantastic!!', '  #GreatForMitchellStudents #GreatForMitchellHamlineStudents', '** We are a family run business, not a big management company, who really cares for our buildings and the tenants so you will receive personal attention and care if you choose to rent from us.', ' Thanks!!', 'Our units feature:', '- 1-BR, LR, Kitchen, Bath, Small dining area', '- Hardwood floors, no carpet', '- Laundry and storage in basement common area', '- Free off street parking lot behind the building (space is limited)', 'For more information and to set up a time to see the available units, please contact the property managers directly and reference this CL ad:', 'Alisa or Brenna', 'Day:', 'show contact info', 'Evening:', 'show contact info', 'Email:  See above "reply to" link.', 'Website for more information:', 'http://www.apts.cc', "1BR's for rent are at 590 Holly Ave, Saint Paul, Minnesota 55102"]
